body:
When I want to export multiple tasks with the same name, the generated code is compiled incorrectly.I'm using the 5.012 tag version. I remember the previous version didn't report errors.
The following is an example:
```verilog
module sub1;
   reg  [127:0] data [7:0];

   export "DPI-C" task write_data;
   task write_data;
   input [2:0] iA;
   input [127:0] iD;
   begin
      data[iA] = iD;
   end
   endtask

endmodule

module sub2;
   reg  [31:0] data [7:0];

   export "DPI-C" task write_data;
   task write_data;
   input [2:0] iA;
   input [31:0] iD;
   begin
      data[iA] = iD;
   end
   endtask
   
endmodule

module top;

   sub1 u_sub1();
   sub2 u_sub2();

   initial begin
      $display("Hello World!");
      $finish;
   end

endmodule
```
The generated code is as follows:
```cpp
